cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.DL

This paper discusses the problem of detecting and preventing the spread of fake media, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed solution involves using machine learning algorithms for pattern recognition (cs.MM) and image processing (cs.CV), as well as blockchain technology for ensuring the integrity and transparency of registered manifests (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of deep learning algorithms (cs.DL) for media synthesis, which further supports the inclusion of these sub-categories in the list.
